# WebPulse — Environment Configuration
# 
#
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your API key.
# If left blank, the system will use the heuristic fallback analyzer
# instead of the LLM — the pipeline will still work, just with a
# less polished summary.
# rename the file to '.env' after adding openai api key here 

OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here
